OL,3,C'I can walk away', says council leader
OL,4,Cafter Reform UK expulsion
OL,6,F"I can walk away today without
OL,7,Fconsequences," declared the embattled
OL,8,Fleader of Staffordshire County Council
OL,9,Fafter having his Reform UK membership
OL,10,Frevoked amid allegations he posted
OL,11,Fracist remarks online.
OL,13,FCllr Ian Cooper made the comments in a
OL,14,FFacebook post on Friday afternoon,
OL,15,Fadding: "The good thing is I don't
OL,16,Fneed to be a politician for the money,
OL,17,Funlike some. I can walk away today
OL,18,Fwithout consequences."
