OL,3,C'I can walk away', says council leader
OL,4,Cafter Reform UK expulsion
OL,6,FHe was replying to a statement from
OL,7,FTamworth's Labour MP Sarah Edwards,
OL,8,Fwriting: "You'll have nothing when you
OL,9,Fare binned in the coming years."
OL,11,FThese remarks mark Cooper's first
OL,12,Fpublic response since campaign group
OL,13,FHope Not Hate accused him of posting a
OL,14,Fseries of racist and bigoted comments
OL,15,Ffrom accounts using his name.
OL,17,FThe group alleges he targeted London
OL,18,Fmayor Sadiq Khan, broadcaster Sangita
OL,19,FMyska and lawyer Dr Shola Mos-
OL,20,FShogbamimu in posts made from online
OL,21,Faccounts.
