OL,3,C'I can walk away', says council leader
OL,4,Cafter Reform UK expulsion
OL,6,FOn Friday evening, Reform UK confirmed
OL,7,Fit had expelled him.
OL,9,FA party spokesperson said: "Following
OL,10,Fan investigation into the failure to
OL,11,Fdeclare social media accounts during
OL,12,Fthe candidate vetting process, Cllr
OL,13,FIan Cooper has had his membership of
OL,14,FReform UK revoked."
