OL,3,C'I can walk away', says council leader
OL,4,Cafter Reform UK expulsion
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Staffordshire
OL,7,FCounty Council said: "Reform UK has
OL,8,Fconfirmed this evening that they have
OL,9,Frevoked the party membership of Ian
OL,10,FCooper, the Leader of Staffordshire
OL,11,FCounty Council.
OL,13,F"Reform UK has announced that Martin
OL,14,FMurray will be the interim leader of
OL,15,Fthe council's Reform UK group. Any
OL,16,Fproposals to nominate a new Leader of
OL,17,Fthe Council will need to be agreed at
OL,18,Fa meeting of Full Council. We will
OL,19,Fwork with the administration on the
OL,20,Fnext steps.
